#<!--NSeriesOfEvents-->a series of events or ideas which are interconnected; a train of events or a train of thought.
#<!--NSeriesOfElectrPulses-->a series of electrical pulses
#<!--NInterconnMechParts-->a set of interconnected mechanical parts like the drive train of a car.
#<!--NGownTail-->that which is drawn along, like the part of a [[gown]] which trails behind the wearer.

